      "releaseNotes": "- New Note Effect: Arpeggiator\n- New Synthesizer: SoundFont Player\n- Added search to the Browser\n- Added drumpad MIDI mapping reset\n- Added parameter labels in Chorus, Flanger and Phaser\n- File and channel names now support Unicode characters\n- Improved Shop waveform rendering performance\n- Fixed a crash when previewing samples\n- Fixed live input notes being cut on playback loop\n- Fixed clips remaining muted after exiting clip preview mode\n- Fixed notes appearing out of bounds in the Piano Roll\n- Fixed drumpad MIDI mapping bugs\n- Fixed Time Spent On Project calculation\n- Fixed repeated scroll gesture on a clip being misinterpreted as a move\n- Fixed context menus appearing misplaced after resizing the grid\n- Fixed intermittent animation glitch in list controls\n- Fixed missing note name labels on the Piano keyboard\n- Fixed horizontal scrolling in dropdown menus\n- Fixed exporting multiple folders from the browser\n- Fixed FLP export not retaining directory structure",
